				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Nametables have to go somewhere specific because the PPU reads them from that place in its memory.<br /><br />Collision tables don't have to go anywhere specific at all, though you most likely want to put them in CPU memory and not PPU memory.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

