					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Your collision table is really specific to your game. There is no best practice. Every game needs something different from this.<br /><br />A game could even read back the nametable over the PPU bus during vblank to get its collision info, but this is a rather advanced and also limited technique.</div>

