				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Though, going further, I would have expected the code to look more like this. I presume you're trying to load collision data from ROM to somewhere in RAM?<br /><br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">; a temporary variable to be used as a pointer<br />.segment &quot;ZEROPAGE&quot;<br />.res tempPointer, 2<br /><br />; the destination of the data<br />.segment &quot;RAM&quot;<br />.res collisionTable, 256<br /><br />.segment &quot;DATA&quot;<br /><br />; pointer table to collision data in ROM<br />; split into low byte and high byte<br /><br />CollisionPointersLow:<br />.db &lt;Collision0<br />.db &lt;Collision1<br />...<br /><br />CollisionPointersHigh:<br />.db &gt;Collision0<br />.db &gt;Collision1<br />...<br /><br />.segment &quot;CODE&quot;<br /><br />; looks up a table based on newScreen<br />; and copies it to the space reserved in RAM<br /><br />LoadCollisionTable:<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; ; look up pointer<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; ldx newScreen<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; lda CollisionPointersLow, X<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; sta tempPointer+0<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; lda CollisionPointersHigh, X<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; sta tempPointer+1<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; ; copy 256 bytes from pointer to collisionTable<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; ldy #0<br />:<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; lda (tempPointer), Y<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; sta collisionTable, Y<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; iny<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; bne :-<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; rts</div></div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

